slation" xml:lang="zh-CN">【沙耶香】将梦想托付给轻轻飘舞的风 启程之时</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">fu wa ri ma u ka ze ni yu me wo no se te ha ji ma ru to ki</span></p><p begin="00:40.859" end="00:44.865" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:40.859" end="00:41.171">期</span><span begin="00:41.171" end="00:41.519">待</span><span begin="00:41.519" end="00:41.641">と</span><span begin="00:41.641" end="00:41.848">不</span><span begin="00:41.848" end="00:42.326">安</span><span begin="00:42.326" end="00:42.655">で</span> <span begin="00:42.776" end="00:43.205">胸</span><span begin="00:43.205" end="00:43.374">が</span><span begin="00:43.374" end="00:43.805">震</span><span begin="00:43.805" end="00:44.168">え</span><span begin="00:44.168" end="00:44.370">て</span><span begin="00:44.370" end="00:44.865">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">【瑠璃乃】心中因期待和不安的轻颤</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ki ta i to fu a n de mu ne ga fu ru e te ru</span></p><p begin="00:45.085" end="00:48.749" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:45.085" end="00:45.308">見</span><span begin="00:45.308" end="00:45.523">慣</span><span begin="00:45.523" end="00:45.783">れ</span><span begin="00:45.783" end="00:45.989">た</span><span begin="00:45.989" end="00:46.198">景</span><span begin="00:46.198" end="00:46.794">色</span> <span begin="00:46.952" end="00:47.153">未</span><span begin="00:47.153" end="00:47.412">来</span><span begin="00:47.412" end="00:47.626">へ</span><span begin="00:47.626" end="00:48.108">移</span><span begin="00:48.108" end="00:48.430">ろ</span><span begin="00:48.430" end="00:48.749">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">【缀理】司空见惯的景色 向着未来推进</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">mi na re ta ke shi ki mi ra i e u tsu ro i</span></p><p begin="00:48.788" end="00:53.147" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:48.788" end="00:49.017">か</span><span begin="00:49.017" end="00:49.239">け</span><span begin="00:49.239" end="00:49.490">が</span><span begin="00:49.490" end="00:49.711">え</span><span begin="00:49.711" end="00:49.800">な</span><span begin="00:49.800" end="00:49.949">い</span><span begin="00:49.949" end="00:50.180">も</span><span begin="00:50.180" end="00:50.365">の</span><span begin="00:50.365" end="00:50.612">に</span><span begin="00:50.612" end="00:50.821">気</span><span begin="00:50.821" end="00:51.329">付</span><span begin="00:51.329" end="00:51.787">い</span><span begin="00:51.787" end="00:51.995">た</span><span begin="00:51.995" end="00:52.260">ん</span><span begin="00:52.260" end="00:52.705">だ</span><span begin="00:52.705" end="00:53.147">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">【慈】也终于明了那无可取代之物</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ka ke ga e na i mo no ni ki zu i ta n da yo</span></p><p begin="00:53.388" end="00:56.840" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:53.388" end="00:53.512">い</span><span begin="00:53.512" end="00:53.644">つ</span><span begin="00:53.644" end="00:54.078">も</span> <span begin="00:54.297" end="00:54.433">そ</span><span begin="00:54.433" end="00:54.572">ば</span><span begin="00:54.572" end="00:54.759">に</span><span begin="00:54.759" end="00:55.026">咲</span><span begin="00:55.026" end="00:55.259">い</span><span begin="00:55.259" end="00:55.482">て</span><span begin="00:55.482" end="00:55.707">い</span><span begin="00:55.707" end="00:55.943">た</span><span begin="00:55.943" end="00:56.181">笑</span><span begin="00:56.181" end="00:56.840">顔</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:56.877" end="00:59.737"><span begin="00:56.877" end="00:56.996">(笑</span><span begin="00:56.996" end="00:57.546">顔</span><span begin="00:57.546" end="00:57.756">が</span><span begin="00:57.756" end="00:57.991">咲</span><span begin="00:57.991" end="00:58.240">く</span> <span begin="00:58.240" end="00:58.886">Bloomin'</span> <span begin="00:58.886" end="00:59.737">story)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">【吟子/小铃/姬芽】笑容盛放 Bloomin' story</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">e ga o ga sa ku Bloomin' story</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">【梢】便是始终在身边绽放的笑容</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">i tsu mo so ba ni sa i te i ta e ga o</span></p><p begin="01:00.258" end="01:03.455" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="01:00.258" end="01:00.556">キ</span><span begin="01:00.556" end="01:00.776">ミ</span><span begin="01:00.776" end="01:01.206">と</span> <span begin="01:01.206" end="01:01.658">刻</span><span begin="01:01.658" end="01:01.731">ん</span><span begin="01:01.731" end="01:01.901">だ</span><span begin="01:01.901" end="01:02.245">瞬</span><span begin="01:02.245" end="01:02.636">間</span><span begin="01:02.636" end="01:03.455">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">【沙耶香】与你一同铭刻的瞬间</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ki mi to ki za n da shu n ka n wo</span></p><p begin="01:04.035" end="01:07.000" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="01:04.035" end="01:04.402">滲</span><span begin="01:04.402" end="01:04.493">ん</span><span begin="01:04.493" end="01:04.865">だ</span> <span begin="01:04.865" end="01:05.405">空</span><span begin="01:05.405" end="01:05.556">に</span><span begin="01:05.556" end="01:05.631">浮</span><span begin="01:05.631" end="01:05.963">か</span><span begin="01:05.963" end="01:06.293">べ</span><span begin="01:06.293" end="01:07.000">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">【瑠璃乃】飞向着氤氲的天空</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ni ji n da so ra ni u ka be te</span></p><p begin="01:07.707" end="01:11.465" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="01:07.707" end="01:07.921">ずっ</span><span begin="01:07.921" end="01:08.184">と</span><span begin="01:08.184" end="01:08.632">ずっ</span><span begin="01:08.632" end="01:08.861">と</span> <span begin="01:08.861" end="01:09.327">忘</span><span begin="01:09.327" end="01:09.797">れ</span><span begin="01:09.797" end="01:10.149">は</span><span begin="01:10.149" end="01:10.251">し</span><span begin="01:10.251" end="01:10.492">な</span><span begin="01:10.492" end="01:10.716">い</span><span begin="01:10.716" end="01:11.177">か</span><span begin="01:11.177" end="01:11.465">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">【花帆】永远永远都不会忘记</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">zu tto zu tto wa su re wa shi na i ka ra</span></p><p begin="01:11.624" end="01:16.405" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="01:11.624" end="01:12.297">約</span><span begin="01:12.297" end="01:12.746">束</span><span begin="01:12.746" end="01:13.005">し</span><span begin="01:13.005" end="01:13.167">よ</span><span begin="01:13.167" end="01:13.349">う</span><span begin="01:13.349" end="01:13.718">よ</span> <span begin="01:13.718" end="01:14.170">こ</span><span begin="01:14.170" end="01:14.397">の</span><span begin="01:14.397" end="01:14.620">場</span><span begin="01:14.620" end="01:14.852">所</span><span begin="01:14.852" end="01:16.405">で</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:16.659" end="01:18.393"><span begin="01:16.659" end="01:17.043">(Thank</span> <span begin="01:17.043" end="01:17.396">you</span> <span begin="01:17.396" end="01:17.608">and</span> <span begin="01:17.608" end="01:18.393">goodbye)</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">许下约定吧 就在这里</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ya ku so ku shi yo u yo ko no ba sho de</span></p><p begin="01:18.334" end="01:21.780" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="01:18.334" end="01:18.569">僕</span><span begin="01:18.569" end="01:18.842">ら</span><span begin="01:19.014" end="01:19.482">未</span><span begin="01:19.482" end="01:19.822">来</span><span begin="01:19.822" end="01:20.155">で</span><span begin="01:20.155" end="01:20.376">花</span><span begin="01:20.376" end="01:20.622">咲</span><span begin="01:20.622" end="01:20.824">く</span><span begin="01:20.824" end="01:21.101">日</span><span begin="01:21.101" end="01:21.319">ま</span><span begin="01:21.319" end="01:21.780">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">【合】在我们迎来未来盛放之日前</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">bo ku ra mi ra i de ha na sa ku hi ma de</span></p><p begin="01:22.024" end="01:25.444" ttm:agent="v1" itunes: